h1= title
p Welcome to #{title}, a sample node.js / express / everyauth / mongodb app for use with Strider & Heroku (and Mongolab).
hr
h3 Add Comment:
form(action='/add_comment', method='post')
  div.clearfix
    div.input
      input(type='textarea', name='body')
  div.actions
    input.btn.primary(type='submit', value='submit')
hr
h3 Comments:
each comment in comments    
  p #{comment.date}  - #{comment.body}  
hr
p
  a(href="/logout") Logout